WEBVTT

00:02:58.520 --> 00:03:02.456
that a study of these children
who were born as designer babies

00:03:02.480 --> 00:03:04.336
indicates they may have some issues,

00:03:04.360 --> 00:03:08.040
like increased aggressiveness
and narcissism.

00:03:09.640 --> 00:03:11.296
But more immediately on your mind

00:03:11.320 --> 00:03:15.016
is some news that you just got
from Jenna's family.

00:03:15.040 --> 00:03:16.536
She's so smart,

00:03:16.560 --> 00:03:19.656
she's now going to be going
to a special school,

00:03:19.680 --> 00:03:22.176
a different school
than your daughter Marianne,

00:03:22.200 --> 00:03:25.936
and this is kind of throwing
your family into a disarray.

00:03:25.960 --> 00:03:27.296
